user.biography:
Make Planet Great Again!
Founded by @coskunenes.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Great Planet in Bali, Indonesia with @demas, and @thegreatplanet. May be an image of nature and tree.

node.text:
🌲 “Hidden in plain sight.” Sometimes you can't see the true #beauty of something until you see it from another #perspective!

Credits: @demas.

#thegreatplanet. Make Planet Great Again!

🚗 How about a trip through quaint, British village in a vintage car? ? Who would you want to discover this place with?

Credits: @monalogue.

#thegreatplanet. Make Planet Great Again!
